'''''The Official Star Wars Fact File'' 87''' was the eighty-seventh issue of ''[[The Official Star Wars Fact File]]'', released on [[August 27]], [[2003]].

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

==Contents==
*The [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]] {{C|GEO 17-20}}
**<small>How the Jedi and the clone troopers battled the Separatists.</small>
*[[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] {{C|ANT 5-8}}
**<small>The head of Wraith Squadron.</small>
*[[Mirith Sinn]] {{C|MIR 1-4}}
**<small>A Rebel commander who opposed the Empire on the world of Phaeda.</small>
*[[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] {{C|EWO 5-8}}
**<small>The leader and the Council of Elders that ''rule'' over the natives of Endor.</small>
*[[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]] {{C|OSS 1-2}}
**<small>The barren, wasted planet that was once the hub of Jedi activity.</small>
*[[Drone barge/Legends|Drone barge]] {{C|BAR 1-2}}
**<small>Droid-directed craft used to carry cargo across the galaxy.</small>
*[[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett's]] [[Boba Fett/Legends#Equipment and gear|weapons and equipment]] {{C|FET 5-6}}
**<small>A rifle customized by Boba Fett for long- and short-range use.</small>
*[[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] [[Gondola Speeder/Legends|Gondola Speeder]] {{C|NAB 7-8}}
**<small>The vessel used by Padme and Anakin to make the trip to Varykino.</small>

